I changed the wording on the CA slightly to remove "postoperative" since the replicating study looked at chemotherapy induced nausea. Also, the postoperative study saw an association during the first few hours, but not long term. Likewise, the chemotherapy study saw an association during the acute phase but not delayed phase. So wording was added to say the association was found "shortly" (undefined) after ondansetron treatment.
